</title>
<subSubSection id="2E08A4F67C12831BC7917CE4FB068970" pageId="null" pageNumber="218" type="description">
<paragraph id="D1A4621FBB358496047F2F4296549A46" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
<emphasis id="8EAEE11BD3788072D1A6A8E8F553BD60" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
<normalizedToken id="D4FA0A60835F983DB1763348F8C80A5C" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="AB82E6182C3D2AB799FF29BDEA84540A" originalValue="gegenständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">gegenstaendig</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
Kelch 
<normalizedToken id="8EE65742F873F5A37975DA1D288A6866" originalValue="röhrig" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">roehrig</normalizedToken>
, kantig, 
<emphasis id="D100F2D4E28FD8B5E38353FF391BF300" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
5 
<normalizedToken id="76C079C3179060434D24F9B0EB68A197" originalValue="zähnig" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">zaehnig</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, 2lippig. 
<emphasis id="4CAEB7137BB9A2B46C1C44160A209304" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
Krone mit weiter 
<normalizedToken id="CDC5C54DCEC0A7D5264E5105EE1548BF" originalValue="Röhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Roehre</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
und 2lippigem Rand; Oberlippe 2teilig; Unterlippe 3teilig, 
<emphasis id="838D090709448596FC8581CBF0B24B93" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
mit 
<normalizedToken id="B99D805512CA99CC036EA5F357027455" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">+/-</normalizedToken>
flachen Abschnitten.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="B9F56147DCB7CCFD4CD4EC7CCF6E51AE" originalValue="Staubblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Staubblaetter</normalizedToken>
4, 2 
<normalizedToken id="4AD163E1440F965E1A6B1C11058F7447" originalValue="längere" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">laengere</normalizedToken>
und 2 
<normalizedToken id="D1E97E22D8DA8D7152AC60F720A382F0" originalValue="kürzere" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">kuerzere</normalizedToken>
. Frucht meist mit 2 Klappen aufspringend.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="543C4AF9CF83B20A778E55BF3A8CD88C" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
Die Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="84DECF62ED9B378CCE2DC9F7FE6415DD" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Phrymaceae" genus="Mimulus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="218" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="3869D2EE38B88CAD7DA33059A7128179" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Mimulus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="DDF88B6C8B808D282A968C478766487E" originalValue="umfaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">umfasst</normalizedToken>
etwa 
<emphasis id="11E9ED92F9F7470AFC592C881EABB2DD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">150 Arten, von denen die meisten im westlichen Nordamerika beheimatet sind.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F9B58EC11BB0819507937F8B7DB4263D" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
<table id="DBA0A64FE7763FE7D1CBD3BD69D262DF" frame="void" pageId="null" pageNumber="218" rules="none" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
<tbody id="501766EEC98DCDD1004DE4A33C3BBE02" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
<tr id="7DFD9B21029D81A24C47ABC9F5C93DA1" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
<td id="0E3529D32AE741BF851F0ABE6025619F" align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="218" valign="top">
<pageBreakToken id="E62EEA76EA5E0952C14289A35EB916A8" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">1</pageBreakToken>
. Pflanze kahl oder mit einzelnen 
<normalizedToken id="4449FA5593BB1B6DDD0D940EC307C771" originalValue="Drüsenhaaren" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Druesenhaaren</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="8C4796EE55A550660E8154461134C103" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Blueten</normalizedToken>
3-4 cm lang; nach der 
<normalizedToken id="ED305B78228FED51A3E28B17A2ED2750" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Bluete</normalizedToken>
mit bauchig erweitertem Kelch
</td>
<td id="0D57A20544DAC1CCFA7A88BD7FFD873C" align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="218" valign="bottom">
<italic id="145EB2D0D25CDC965A0FB9B0152AABC3" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">M. guttatus</italic>
(Nr. 1)
</td>
</tr>
<tr id="BE785EA0D772039AA8E4104DAB32BC0A" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">
<td id="9F409B661F104066DB31F29E210CD06B" align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="218" valign="top">
1*. Pflanze 
<normalizedToken id="5DD2BC76F2A13E3C988039C7F5BD1CC8" originalValue="drüsig-klebrig" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">druesig-klebrig</normalizedToken>
behaart; 
<normalizedToken id="7F1EE9F4099CEB36D0563ED61F5A86C6" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Blueten</normalizedToken>
1,4-2 cm lang; Kelch nach der 
<normalizedToken id="468B8D692610CA23DF11E6FA8621FEB0" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">Bluete</normalizedToken>
nicht bauchig erweitert
</td>
<td id="5067838C88A3A71E72ED1F633BA83A25" align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="218" valign="bottom">
<italic id="CCB805B87BB5ED01988A3F4CAF997FD7" pageId="null" pageNumber="218">M. moschatus</italic>
(Nr. 2)
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</paragraph>
